title: Winamp v5.666 build 3516 + Key + ALL ADDONS, SKINS, & VISUAL
description:
This is the most complete copy of Winamp and its entire legacy that youll find on the internet. 
Inside youll find the latest version of Winamp (as of writing thats v5.666 build 3516) with a key + its important patches that fix several issues + Everything that was on the old (now defunt) Winamp plugin page neatly organized as they were on the website.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 

Step 1) Install Winamp by doubleclicking on winamp5666_full_all.exe

Step 2) Open Winamp's settings panel and enter serial from Serial.txt into registration section of settings.

Step 3) Double click on "Jump_to_File_Extra_v1_33_(Build_1216).exe" and in_mp3__4_103__winamp5666_3512.exe, they are update patches that fix several bugs in Winamp.

Step 4) Install whatever plugin/skin/visualisation you want!

Step 5) Enjoy!


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Note:


The plugins archive is reupload of a torrent i found on TPB a few days before Winamp's AOL owned page was to be shutdown for good. The original uploader collected every single plugin, visualization, skin, language pack, you name it, and organized them as they were exactly on the addons page.

Im not sure why it was deleted off TPB, but i got it before it was gone, and here i upload it for all, for whoever wants them.


Bear in mind that the Winamp plugin page was rarely updated and Winamp itself over the years natively implemented most of the important features third party plugins added. Alot dont even work with the latest Winamp version, and some can even crash Winamp. Some of the really good plugins that are irreplaceable (like the input plugins) have been updated but on the developers page, not the Winamp addons page, so the plugins you find here are probably not the most recent version. Heck some are even a decade old.
